Ramakrishna & the Forgetful Farmer - Yogi Stories

Ramakrishna & the Forgetful Farmer

Jun 13, 2025

View in app

Someone recently told me that they very often feel guilty they're not doing enough, even though their meditations are going very well. So I reminded them of this beautiful story, which I understand was told by Ramakrishna, the king of bhakti devotion. Reminding us what a grand feat it is to remember the Higher Self, and pursue the Higher Self, in such a crazy mixed up world as this.

Blissings and love to you! See you in a few hours for the Satsang.
